steps.name: Open METCAL Runtime and enter valid login and password for MC user
click on the Select DUT button
enter the "AutomationTestAsset" and click ok button
navigate to the Run window and click run button
enter "77" and "37" and click ok button
on the Post-Prompt screen select "As-Found" dropdown and enter "This is automated test note" to the textbox
get text from the MetCal Information and asssert "Data exported successfully"
Open METCAL Runtime and enter valid login and password for MC user
verify that for MC user "RUN" and "CONFIGURE" tabs is enabled
Open METCAL Runtime and enter valid login and password for Admin user
verify that for MC user RUN and CONFIGURE tabs is disabled
